revision.text:
'''Shinto Honkyoku''' (Shintō Taikyō) is a [[Japan]]ese [[Shintoism|Shintoist]] organization. It was established by Meiji officials in 1873. <ref>http://www.adherents.com/Na/Na_602.html</ref> It is recognized officially. <ref>http://www.joyofsects.com/world/shinto.shtml</ref> Its headquarters are in [[Tokyo]]. <ref>http://eos.kokugakuin.ac.jp/modules/xwords/entry.php?entryID=652</ref> It has shrines. <ref>http://www.novelguide.com/a/discover/ear_01/ear_01_00184.html</ref> [[Tenrikyo]] used to be under its jurisdiction. <ref>http://www.tenrikyo.or.jp/en/newsletter/html/tt5/genten_kyoten.html</ref>
==References== {{reflist}}
